handshaking.statement:
Let N=|Fib_w(z)|, A=|A_SP(z)|, P=P_multi(z), N_ord=sum_{multi pencils} k(k−1). Then:
  N_ord = sum_v deg(v)  (sum over vertices of ordered out-degree in the directed complete orientation of each pencil clique);
  A ≤ N_ord          (each A_SP vertex has deg ≥ 1);
  P ≤ floor(A/2)     (each multi pencil has k ≥ 2);
  P ≤ floor(N/2)     (A ≤ N and previous);
  A ≤ pack_ceil · P ≤ pack_ceil · floor(N/2);
  A ≤ N;
  N_ord ≤ (pack_ceil−1) · A ≤ (pack_ceil−1) · N.
